{"tid":1857613,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"「聲控撚入」關於聲優，大家點面對呢種情況？好徬徨...","createTime":"2020-02-02T09:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T14:04:12.000Z","uid":157483,"like":3,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"afce0896fb0f25681af530f3006d52e9f5d91097","tid":1857613,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:13:10.000Z","msg":"大家有冇試過好鍾意一把聲或者某個角色<br />\n然後呢種聲比左某種感覺或者形象你，甚至會腦補呢把聲應該會係個點樣既人<br />\n或者你好鍾意某個角色，同時覺得把聲配得好好，聲人合一 好完美<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但<br />\n結果無意中或者手賤走去search聲優既資料，然後見到相.... 同原本自己想像把聲既形象完全唔同（eg 生得好7，肥婆肥佬，年紀好大etc）甚至幻滅哂.. 到底呢種情況應該點樣面對或者調節？<br />\n<br />\n以我為例，我曾經好鍾意如月千早，有一日手賤去google今井麻美.... 一下子唔知點接受，同自己既感覺落差太大。搞到我以後再聽呢把聲或者望住如月千早個樣，都會諗起今井麻美個樣..."},{"pid":"ed4f31bc6056e1c3ef2f36d083ee8a7f35e46914","tid":1857613,"uid":79756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:13:46.000Z","msg":"俾對鞋你聞下？"},{"pid":"c6e4f5c68fb22bfc68e55c0d8af07d1c3b0b2615","tid":1857613,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:18:22.000Z","msg":"我諗實有人都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ec7506b37087fc68a2c3bb03de2a20beb6ee0b","tid":1857613,"uid":118709,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:20:57.000Z","msg":"下...淑女好可愛喎...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n垃圾引戰post <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"6b75e091059b0f60b0a66c09d7571d57ead974f1","tid":1857613,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"83ec7506b37087fc68a2c3bb03de2a20beb6ee0b","tid":1857613,"uid":118709,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:20:57.000Z","msg":"下...淑女好可愛喎...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n垃圾引戰post <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:23:52.000Z","msg":"咁無聊既野都有得引戰，你既人生都幾無聊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3cc